8
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:51,976
[Queen of Darkness]

9
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[Episode 3]

10
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:08,176
How is she this good?

11
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,760
Run, run! Go!

12
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:13,960
[Jiang Meng]

13
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,656
I got such good moves.

14
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,696
Totally not like a housewife.

15
00:01:18,720 --> 00:01:20,640
Could I be someone else?

16
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:30,536
No clue about who sent those people

17
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,576
to attack me last night.

18
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:34,880
And I still can't recall my past.

19
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:37,376
But stuck with
such a terrible Song family.

20
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,456
Plus that shady cop Huo Xiao.

21
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,040
How do I get out of this mess?

22
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,576
I found out

23
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:48,496
the daughter-in-law of the Song family
is indeed An Ning.

24
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,016
But An Ning is weak-tempered.

25
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,576
She was bullied all the time
in the Song family

26
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,416
and just endured it quietly.

27
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,440
Never says a word.

28
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,376
If she were Ye Ying,

29
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:03,840
there should be a
Qingyun tattoo on her back.

30
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:26,040
♪ Hold me tight,
let the darkness drown me ♪

31
00:02:26,370 --> 00:02:33,440
♪ Even one second of truth is enough
to lose myself in it ♪

32
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:38,400
Even if Ti Cha
cheated with your best friend,

33
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,856
you shouldn't look this heartbroken.

34
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:43,216
Inspector Huo,
you aren't just after the truth.

35
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,960
And also in charge of
mending broken hearts?

36
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,040
Your clothes are wet.

37
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,760
You'll get sick if you don't change.

38
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,480
Please keep your distance.

39
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,616
Whatever I want,

40
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:06,560
they'll hand it over without hesitation.

41
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,320
Don't even think about it.

42
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,080
The missing Ye Ying.

43
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:28,080
The amnesiac An Ning.

44
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,576
Was it just an accident,

45
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,680
or a well-planned coincidence?

46
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,000
Inspector.

47
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,400
This is the original file
on Ye Hong's death report.

48
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,096
As you instructed,

49
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,696
everyone who knew about Ye Hong's death

50
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,840
has been placed under watch.

51
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:49,280
The fish won't bite.

52
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,520
It means the bait isn't big enough.

53
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,440
From now on,

54
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,720
Ye Hong has come back to life.

55
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,800
Let's see

56
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,120
how tough.

57
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,600
Ye Ying's heart is.

58
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,736
According to reliable sources,

59
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,136
Ye Hong, the gang leader,

60
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,576
was attacked within his gang

61
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,736
and seriously injured a few days ago.

62
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,016
He was badly hurt but still alive.

63
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,360
He's now being treated
at a private hospital.

64
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,296
Sources close to the case revealed

65
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,696
that this incident is highly likely

66
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,280
an act of deliberate revenge.

67
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,096
Those reporters are pretty capable.

68
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,816
I kept everything so low‑key.

69
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,880
Yet they still managed to
dig out the story.

70
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,920
What are you thinking about?

71
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,457
So engrossed.

72
00:04:50,481 --> 00:04:51,536
What I'm thinking about

73
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,560
is none of your business.

74
00:04:58,080 --> 00:05:02,040
You demanded 24-hour close protection.

75
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:06,360
So of course I have to
keep an eye on you.

76
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,560
Look.

77
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,120
The eggs are about to burn.

78
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,656
I'm warning you.

79
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,576
Don't mess around.

80
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,600
Be careful, or I'll...

81
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,200
You'll do what?

82
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:27,980
♪ Falling in love ♪

83
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,480
Kill me

84
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,936
or arrest me?

85
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:38,520
♪ Catch me, I'm falling for you ♪

86
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,640
Cut the smooth talk.

87
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,960
I truly hate what you do.

88
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,700
♪ Everyday, every night ♪

89
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,000
But why is there

90
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,600
a hint of panic in your eyes?

91
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:06,960
Don't misunderstand.

92
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,160
I was out of line yesterday.

93
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,240
I'm here to apologize.

94
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,040
I don't accept

95
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,760
an after-the-fact apology.

96
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,400
It's okay.

97
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,320
I can wait.

98
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:54,040
I have plenty of patience

99
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,320
to wait for your forgiveness.

100
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:10,040
[Century Hospital]

101
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,536
[Operating Room/Ward]

102
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,560
Inspector.

103
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,360
Ye Ying still hasn't shown up.

104
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,577
Could it be…

105
00:07:21,601 --> 00:07:23,160
Our judgment is wrong?

106
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,760
[Operating Room/Ward]

107
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,360
She's here.

108
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,480
We'll have the answer soon.

109
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:45,200
[Dr. Aamir Kan; Patient: Ye Hong]

110
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,016
Police investigation.

111
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,040
Go.

112
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:19,840
Neuroscience Department.

113
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,096
She's here for a follow-up exam.

114
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,680
The appointment time is…

115
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,697
[Patient Info: An Ning,
Date of Report: 2025.09.20]

116
00:08:25,721 --> 00:08:26,736
Three days ago?

117
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:27,760
But back then…

118
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:30,320
We hadn't even started planning yet.

119
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,760
[Century Hospital, Aamir Kan]

120
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,360
What do you do?

121
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,320
Making rounds.

122
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,320
It seems the mastermind

123
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,760
couldn't wait to silence Ye Hong.

124
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,400
So that means.

125
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,736
An Ning's appearance
was really a coincidence.

126
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:25,760
Anyway.

127
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,680
Keep tracking.

128
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:29,200
Ye Ying's whereabouts.

129
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:30,880
Okay.

130
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,136
Mom, Dad.

131
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,480
[Elder Sister-in-Law] We're back.

132
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,800
Hey sweet girl, you're here.

133
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:46,176
I came back as soon as you called.

134
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,560
Grandma, Xuan.

135
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:48,920
So sweet.

136
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,640
Mom.

137
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,696
This is for you.

138
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,960
It's pure gold.

139
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,600
Thank you, my dear girl.

140
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,360
Dad.

141
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,000
I specially bought this

142
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,336
at a high price

143
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:03,160
from Cuba.

144
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,000
It's a limited edition now.

145
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,376
Good.

146
00:10:06,377 --> 00:10:26,377
